1. Introduction

Welcome to the [Your Company Name] Digital Enrollment Platform.

This guide explains how to integrate your system to:

Submit digital enrollment requests

Retrieve enrollment status on demand (Pull Model)

Receive automated status updates (Push Model)

All APIs are secured using OAuth 2.0 (Client Credentials Grant).

This document is designed to enable quick and seamless onboarding.

Welcome to the [Your Company Name] Digital Enrollment Platform.

Our Digital Enrollment APIs provide secure, scalable integration for submitting and processing enrollments. They support real-time and scheduled workflows for seamless connection with your applications, portals, or backend systems.

Through this integration, you can:

Submit digital enrollment requests

Retrieve enrollment status on demand (Pull Model)

Receive automated status updates through scheduled batch notifications (Push Model)

All APIs follow REST principles, use JSON payloads over HTTPS, and are secured using OAuth 2.0 (Client Credentials Grant).

This guide provides the information needed for onboarding, authentication, API usage, and status handling to help your teams integrate quickly and efficiently.

